1.在Ambari server上，执行
    ```java
    ambari-server stop
    ambari-server reset
    yum erase ambari-server -y
    ```
2.在ambari agent上执行
    ```java
    ambari-agent stop
    yum erase ambari-agent  -y
    ```
3.在所有节点依次执行,
    ```java
    #清除ambari相关的rpm
    ./Ambari-uninstall-ambari.sh
    #清除hdp相关的rpm
    ./Ambari-uninstall-hdp.sh
    #清除创建的用户
    ./Ambari-uninstall-deluser.sh
    #清除残留文件夹(可能有遗漏)
    ./Ambari-uninstall-deldir.sh
    ```